      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions used for validation must be documented with sufficient detail to replicate boundary conditions in the CFD model, including fluid temperature, hematocrit, and pump speed.",
      "rationale": "FDA pump experimental dataset (Hariharan et al.) documents fluid temperature (37°C), bovine blood hematocrit (33%), and all five flow-speed operating points. Boundary conditions in the CFD model are traceable to the published experimental protocol. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
